CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,FThe captain of a Russian shadow fleet
OL,7,Fvessel carrying 98,000 tonnes of oil
OL,8,Fwhich was intercepted by British
OL,9,Ftroops in the English Channel has
OL,10,Fappeared in court charged with
OL,11,Fbreaching sanctions.
OL,13,FIndian national Ajay Pant has been
OL,14,Fcharged with directly or indirectly
OL,15,Fsupplying or delivering by ship
OL,16,Fprohibited oil or oil products from
OL,17,FRussia to a third country in June
OL,18,F2026, in contravention of Regulation
OL,19,F46Z9B of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU
OL,20,FExit) Regulations 2019.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,FThe 38-year-old appeared at
OL,7,FSouthampton Magistrates' Court by
OL,8,Fvideolink from Bournemouth police
OL,9,Fstation on Tuesday for a preliminary
OL,10,Fhearing during which he spoke to
OL,11,Fconfirm his name and date of birth and
OL,12,Fgave his address as being in India.
OL,14,FHe also gave no indication of his plea
OL,15,Fand his solicitor James Diamond
OL,16,Frequested the case be sent to the
OL,17,Fcrown court.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,FDistrict Judge David Robinson, who
OL,7,Fappeared on the videolink from
OL,8,FPortsmouth, sent the case for a plea
OL,9,Fand trial preparation hearing at
OL,10,FBournemouth Crown Court on July 16 and
OL,11,Fremanded Pant in custody until then.
OL,13,FThe court heard that the oil tanker
OL,14,Fwas part of Russia's "clandestine
OL,15,Ffleet of 700 ships" which acted as its
OL,16,F"lifeline" by transporting 75% of its
OL,17,Foil and helping fund the war against
OL,18,FUkraine.
OL,26,@vD@VOUwD@SO]xD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,FRoyal Marine commandos and officers
OL,7,Ffrom the National Crime Agency (NCA)
OL,8,Fseized the tanker Smyrtos in the
OL,9,FChannel early on Sunday in the first
OL,10,FUK-led operation to capture a
OL,11,Fsanctioned vessel and it has since
OL,12,Fbeen formally prevented from leaving
OL,13,Fthe UK.
OL,15,FThe 24 crew members, from Georgia and
OL,16,FIndia, remain on board the ship, which
OL,17,Fis anchored off Weymouth in Dorset.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,FJoanne Jakymec, chief Crown prosecutor
OL,7,Ffor the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,8,F(CPS), said: "The CPS has decided to
OL,9,Fprosecute Ajay Pant for breaching
OL,10,FRussian sanctions following a National
OL,11,FCrime Agency investigation and the
OL,12,Fseizure of the shadow oil tanker, MV
OL,13,FSmyrtos, travelling through the
OL,14,FEnglish Channel over the last weekend."
OL,16,FMr Diamond said: "Without any
OL,17,Findication of potential sentence,
OL,18,Fgiven the severity of the matter, I
OL,19,Fwould submit the crown court would be
OL,20,Fthe appropriate venue."
OL,26,@pD@NOUvD@gO]xD@ROU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,FVarun Chuni, prosecuting, said: "The
OL,7,FCrown says this is a matter that
OL,8,Fshould be sent to the crown court,
OL,9,Fthere are no sentencing guidelines,
OL,10,Fthe offence carries a maximum
OL,11,Fpunishment of 10 years."
OL,13,FHe added: "On the morning of June 14,
OL,14,FRoyal Marines and the National Crime
OL,15,FAgency boarded the oil tanker MV
OL,16,FSmyrtos, that vessel had entered UK
OL,17,Fterritorial waters without a
OL,18,Flegitimate flag.
OL,26,@nD@aOUsD@XO]uD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,F"The MV Smyrtos is an oil tanker that
OL,7,Fis utilised by the Russian shadow
OL,8,Ffleet, the shadow fleet is a
OL,9,Fdescription given to the clandestine
OL,10,Ffleet of tankers that Russia used to
OL,11,Ftransport its oil around the world.
OL,13,F"They operate under a flag of
OL,14,Fconvenience, the genuine owners of
OL,15,Fthose tankers are very difficult to
OL,16,Ftrace.
OL,18,F"In order to deceive law enforcement,
OL,19,Fthey turn off tracking transponders
OL,20,Fand they regularly change flags and
OL,21,Fbroadcast false locations."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,FHe said that the MV Smyrtos was
OL,7,Fdesignated under UK sanctions on
OL,8,FRussia in 2025 which "were introduced
OL,9,Fto place pressure on Russia and its
OL,10,Feconomy".
OL,12,FHe said: "It's known it was in Russia
OL,13,Fon June 5 2026 and departed Russian
OL,14,Fterritorial waters.
OL,16,F"Its movements were monitored, it then
OL,17,Fentered UK territorial waters, east of
OL,18,FMargate, on June 13, flying the flag
OL,19,Fof Cameroon.
OL,26,@pD@VOUrD@HO]tD@JOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,F"The master of that vessel has been
OL,7,Fidentified as the defendant. He is an
OL,8,FIndian national and he was arrested on
OL,9,Fthe evening of June 14 and is
OL,10,Fcurrently in custody.
OL,12,F"He's suspected to be master of that
OL,13,Fvessel, essentially in charge of it.
OL,15,F"The amount of oil being carried is
OL,16,Fsubstantial, it is thought to be
OL,17,F98,000 tonnes of oil, clearly that is
OL,18,Fa significant amount. As to its value,
OL,19,Fit's uncontroversial to say it's of
OL,20,Fvery significant value."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,FMr Chuni added: "This is clearly a
OL,7,Fmatter of great national interest,
OL,8,Finternational interest as well, the
OL,9,Fshadow fleet is a significant matter."
OL,11,FHe said that the MV Smyrtos was one of
OL,12,F700 ships used by Russia as part of
OL,13,Fits shadow fleet which transports 75%
OL,14,Fof its oil and added: "It's an
OL,15,Fessential, critical lifeline for the
OL,16,Fcountry.
OL,18,F"The money generated from that shadow
OL,19,Ffleet is being used to fund Russia's
OL,20,Fwar in Ukraine."
OL,26,@nD@QOUqD@fO]vD@WOUzD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,FMr Diamond said that his client, who
OL,7,Fhad no previous convictions in any
OL,8,Fcountry, was only an employee of the
OL,9,Fvessel's owner and was "simply
OL,10,Ffollowing orders".
OL,12,FHe said: "The defendant is very clear,
OL,13,Fit was not his choice where this
OL,14,Fvessel was going, it was not his
OL,15,Fchoice what this vessel was going to
OL,16,Fbe carrying, he was simply following
OL,17,Forders from those within the country."
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@QO]tD@JOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,FHe added: "The defendant is not a
OL,7,FRussian national or has received any
OL,8,Fmoney or benefits from Russia, he is
OL,9,Fsimply an employee doing his job and
OL,10,Ffinding himself before a British
OL,11,Fcourt."
OL,13,FRemanding Pant in custody, District
OL,14,FJudge Robinson said: "Having
OL,15,Fconsidered these matters, I do think
OL,16,Fbecause of the nature and seriousness
OL,17,Fof the offences you are charged with
OL,18,Fand the likely penalty if you are
OL,19,Fconvicted, there are substantial
OL,20,Fgrounds to fear that you could abscond.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@GO]vD@VOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781635704
OL,3,CCaptain of seized Russian shadow fleet
OL,4,Cship appears in court
OL,6,F"You will therefore be remanded in
OL,7,Fcustody until your next hearing in the
OL,8,Fcrown court."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/13
